OL,7,FThe deaths of two young children in a
OL,8,Ffire at their home was "a tragic and
OL,9,Fdevastating accident", a coroner has
OL,10,Fconcluded.
OL,12,FLouis Busuioc, five, and his little
OL,13,Fsister Desire, three, both died just
OL,14,Fdays after being rescued from a huge
OL,15,Ffire at their home in Coronation
OL,16,FCrescent in Preston.
OL,18,FThe blaze happened after the children
OL,19,Fhad been playing with a lighter,
OL,20,Fcatching the sofa alight, the inquest
OL,21,Ffound.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
