OL,7,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,8,Fhouse after a neighbour spotted a fire
OL,9,Fin the front living room at 7.52pm on
OL,10,F8 April 2022.
OL,12,FThe two children had been upstairs
OL,13,Fwith their mum, Lorena, who was
OL,14,Fasleep, while their Dad Lucian was at
OL,15,Fwork, the inquest was told.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
