OL,4,C'accidentally started by one of the
OL,5,Cyoungsters'
OL,7,FThe inquest heard the children used a
OL,8,Fcoat hanger to unlock the bedroom door
OL,9,Fand go downstairs, it is thought one
OL,10,Fof them then began playing with a
OL,11,Flighter, which accidentally set fire
OL,12,Fto the sofa.
OL,14,FThe house was quickly overcome with
OL,15,Fsmoke and heat and when Lorena was
OL,16,Fwoken by the sound of the smoke alarm
OL,17,Fshe desperately tried to push her
OL,18,Fchildren out of an upstairs window.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
