OL,3,CFire that killed two children
OL,4,C'accidentally started by one of the
OL,5,Cyoungsters'
OL,7,FThe terrified children refused and so
OL,8,FLorena climbed out of the window first
OL,9,Fin the hope of pulling them out after
OL,10,Fher.
OL,12,FSeveral neighbours made a makeshift
OL,13,Fplatform to try and reach Lorena and
OL,14,Fbegged her to jump from the window
OL,15,Fledge. Believing that someone would
OL,16,Fthen go and rescue her children Lorena
OL,17,Fjumped to safety.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
