OL,3,CFire that killed two children
OL,4,C'accidentally started by one of the
OL,5,Cyoungsters'
OL,7,FHe said "We see very few children who
OL,8,Fmake it to intensive care following
OL,9,Fsmoke inhalation," Dr Nicholls said.
OL,11,F"The damage is done even before
OL,12,Fchildren can be removed from a house
OL,13,Ffire. My personal feeling is that
OL,14,Fnothing would have altered the outcome
OL,15,Ffor these children unfortunately."
OL,17,FThe inquest heard from many police
OL,18,Fofficers, paramedics and firefighters
OL,19,Fwho dealt with the chaotic scene at
OL,20,FCoronation Crescent on the evening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
