OL,5,Cyoungsters'
OL,7,FArea Coroner Chris Long concluded that
OL,8,Falthough there had been some delay to
OL,9,Fthe deployment of paramedics, arriving
OL,10,Fsooner would "not have made any
OL,11,Fdifference", given Dr Nicholls'
OL,12,Fevidence, and he praised the emergency
OL,13,Fservices for their efforts in trying
OL,14,Fto save the children.
OL,16,F"Whilst I have found some elements of
OL,17,Fthe response were not as they should
OL,18,Fhave been I have not found that any of
OL,19,Fthose elements have contributed to
OL,20,Fdeath," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
