OL,5,Cyoungsters'
OL,7,FThe coroner also ruled that the fire
OL,8,Fhad been started, accidentally, by one
OL,9,Fof the children. However, he added
OL,10,Fthat "an inquest is not about
OL,11,Fattributing blame".
OL,13,FHe added: "Children experiment. I am
OL,14,Fsure many in the courtroom will
OL,15,Fremember being told by their parents
OL,16,Fnot to play with matches or indeed
OL,17,Fsaying that as a parent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
