OL,3,CFire that killed two children
OL,4,C'accidentally started by one of the
OL,5,Cyoungsters'
OL,7,F"They did not intend it to catch fire.
OL,8,FIn short, they accidentally set fire
OL,9,Fto the sofa, which led to the fire
OL,10,Fstarting."
OL,12,FReturning a conclusion of accidental
OL,13,Fdeath, the coroner said that both
OL,14,Fchildren "died on 11 April 2022, at
OL,15,FRoyal Manchester Children's Hospital
OL,16,Fin Manchester as a result of hypoxic
OL,17,Fischemic brain injury caused by smoke
OL,18,Finhalation as a result of a fire".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
